# Extension Rules

## Stack

WXT + React + TypeScript + Manifest V3. Side panel is primary report UI.

## File Placement

- DOM / URLs → `platform-adapters/douyin-web.adapter.ts` only
- Orchestration → `entrypoints/background.ts`
- Recording → `entrypoints/offscreen/` (user gesture required)
- UI → `entrypoints/sidepanel/`, `popup/`

## PlatformAdapter

Implement interface from `packages/platform-core`. Layered extraction: URL → anchors → semantic DOM → selectors → manual fallback.

## Capture

- `tabCapture` / `MediaRecorder` only after explicit Analyze click
- Never auto-start recording on page load or navigation
- Host permission: `*.douyin.com` for V1

